# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiep4.rpy:14
translate chinese jamiep4_1560ee7a:

    # gnd "My friends haven't always been there for me in the past."
    gnd "过去我的朋友们并不总是支持我。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiep4.rpy:15
translate chinese jamiep4_9a6e6558:

    # gnd "My family though - my dad and my grandparents."
    gnd "但我的家人——我爸爸和祖父母。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiep4.rpy:16
translate chinese jamiep4_46d06393:

    # gnd "They've always had my back, every step of the way."
    gnd "他们一直支持我，每一步都陪在我身边。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiep4.rpy:20
translate chinese jamiep4_24a9b5a3:

    # gnd "You have family though too. Your dad, Lisa, Suzy."
    gnd "不过你也有家人啊。你爸爸、丽莎、苏西。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiep4.rpy:21
translate chinese jamiep4_92cb41d7:

    # pc "My dad used to be there for me."
    pc "我爸爸以前一直支持我。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiep4.rpy:22
translate chinese jamiep4_02573ba2:

    # pc "But I guess I messed that up when I moved away."
    pc "但我想是我搬走后搞砸了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiep4.rpy:23
translate chinese jamiep4_8ce5d3ab:

    # pc "Now he's just gone."
    pc "现在他已经不在了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiep4.rpy:24
translate chinese jamiep4_f9f09560:

    # pc "Lisa and Suzy are okay, but they don't really feel like family."
    pc "丽莎和苏西还行，但感觉不像家人。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiep4.rpy:25
translate chinese jamiep4_5bdc15a9:

    # gnd "It'll get better. I know it will."
    gnd "情况会好转的。我知道会的。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiep4.rpy:26
translate chinese jamiep4_b83bf564:

    # pc "It's not bad. I have a lot of people that I care about."
    pc "其实还不错。我有好多在乎的人。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiep4.rpy:27
translate chinese jamiep4_9261372e:

    # gnd "You just don't have that person who you know will always be there for you no matter what?"
    gnd "只是你没有那个无论发生什么都会一直支持你的人？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiep4.rpy:28
translate chinese jamiep4_f9588d6c:

    # pc "Yeah. That's it."
    pc "是啊。就是这样。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiep4.rpy:29
translate chinese jamiep4_c682df5b:

    # gnd "You'll find that person."
    gnd "你会找到那个人的。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiep4.rpy:30
translate chinese jamiep4_7a4224f6:

    # gnd "Trust me. You'll know when you do."
    gnd "相信我。当你遇到时，你自然会知道。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiep4.rpy:34
translate chinese jamiep4_bb04ef94:

    # gnd "He's not a dick."
    gnd "他不是混蛋。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiep4.rpy:35
translate chinese jamiep4_55c86dee:

    # gnd "He's just protective of me. He cares about me a lot."
    gnd "他只是很保护我。他非常在乎我。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiep4.rpy:36
translate chinese jamiep4_e7c13a92:

    # gnd "Don't call him that again."
    gnd "别再这么叫他了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiep4.rpy:37
translate chinese jamiep4_a9a6d45d:

    # pc "Okay, sorry. He just hasn't been too nice to me."
    pc "好的，对不起。他只是最近对我不太好。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiep4.rpy:39
translate chinese jamiep4_b641207b:

    # gnd "He'll come around eventually. Give him time."
    gnd "他迟早会回心转意的。给他点时间。"

